title: Bookflix
description: A fun site for searching the name of a movie, which will then return books related to the movie and allow the user to check past searches.

title: Dear Diary
description: An app that allows users to create an account, enter recorded logs, and log in and review past logs.

title: Dog Quiz
description: A simple quiz using basic javascript and html about dogs and dog breeds.

title: Day Planner
description: An app that allows users to set reminders per hour of the work day, and alerts users when that hour is over. Very helpful for scheduling during the work day.

title: Budget Tracker
description: An app that allows the users to input transactions in order to keep on top of their budget. Has offline functionality.

title: Employee Directory
description: An app built in React that finds employees by the letters searched.
